
Simple java program which is used to read file with user selected files. 

Open project in the Eclipse platform.
Add window builder plugin for user interface.
Add JUnit Plugin for unit test run correctly.

About Program:
Select file from computer.
Read it in the Text Area.
Show statistics using show statistic button.
User can write in the file.
User also remove the content of the file by using Remove Content.

About Unit Test
replace 	  String path = "C:\\Users\\faria\\Desktop\\testone.txt";
path must be according to your PC path.

NOTE:
Do not create temporary folder because it is a bug which is not deleting the existing files. 
Failed to delete temp directory: https://github.com/spring-io/initializr/issues/862 (could be potential junit bug)

Output screen is present in the image folder.